00:24:43.501 --> 00:24:44.000
That's fine.

00:24:44.000 --> 00:24:45.249
That's great alternative text.

00:24:45.249 --> 00:24:47.040
That's exactly what it is.

00:24:47.040 --> 00:24:50.350
The big picture where the
kid was standing-- nothing.

00:24:50.350 --> 00:24:50.990
It's blank.

00:24:50.990 --> 00:24:52.700
There's no alternative text.

00:24:52.700 --> 00:24:56.370
And that's OK, because that
image is purely decorative.

00:24:56.370 --> 00:24:58.140
Its presence there
doesn't add anything

00:24:58.140 --> 00:25:00.230
to the value of
the content, and I

00:25:00.230 --> 00:25:02.640
don't want to take somebody
on your screen reader

00:25:02.640 --> 00:25:06.110
and have them listen to this
long description of kid happily

00:25:06.110 --> 00:25:07.924
running after a
soccer ball, and right

00:25:07.924 --> 00:25:09.590
after I took this
picture, he fell down,

00:25:09.590 --> 00:25:11.506
and we all laughed, and
