00:25:11.506 --> 00:25:13.690
and we apologized for an hour.

00:25:13.690 --> 00:25:15.510
Because that's unnecessary.

00:25:15.510 --> 00:25:17.450
You might also
note that there are

00:25:17.450 --> 00:25:23.040
icons in the navigation across
the top and on the left side.

