00:25:55.550 --> 00:25:59.710
and Print Screen drops your
rate and a high contrast mode.

00:25:59.710 --> 00:26:03.040
And what that will do is
totally swap out your background

00:26:03.040 --> 00:26:03.780
images.

00:26:03.780 --> 00:26:05.180
It removes the
background images,

00:26:05.180 --> 00:26:06.900
and it also replaces
all the colors

00:26:06.900 --> 00:26:09.570
throughout all of your
stylesheets-- text colors,

00:26:09.570 --> 00:26:12.200
the background
colors, et cetera.

00:26:12.200 --> 00:26:16.510
So here's that same
page, ready to go.

00:26:16.510 --> 00:26:18.310
There it is Windows
high contrast mode.

00:26:18.310 --> 00:26:21.360
Background images have
gone away-- not a problem.

00:26:21.360 --> 00:26:23.920
I know this because I also
