00:27:50.870 --> 00:27:52.150
pretty straightforward.

00:27:52.150 --> 00:27:54.940
We're not losing anything there.

00:27:54.940 --> 00:27:58.784
Test for color blindness
and color contrast.

00:27:58.784 --> 00:28:00.200
Make sure there's
enough contrast.

00:28:00.200 --> 00:28:01.574
This doesn't just
help the people

00:28:01.574 --> 00:28:03.800
who are using the
screens in sunlight,

00:28:03.800 --> 00:28:06.370
but it helps
potentially everybody.

00:28:06.370 --> 00:28:08.640
Are the hyperlinks and
menus still visible?

00:28:08.640 --> 00:28:11.230
If they aren't, you do
have a problem there.

